{"tid":1074493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【宮鬥劇禁唔完】廣電總局最新「限古令」 全面禁播所有古裝劇，包括網劇","createTime":"2019-03-23T12:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T12:11:13.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ba547671870fc244c0557cb03d1513a61e03fe07","tid":1074493,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T12:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190323/large/1553332711_d5f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190323%2Flarge%2F1553332711_d5f2.jpg&h=d01af02f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190323/large/1553331038_af9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190323%2Flarge%2F1553331038_af9a.jpg&h=511e6e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸廣電總局去年開始禁播宮鬥劇後，昨日公佈最新的「限古令」，要所有古裝劇全面消失，根據規定，即日起至6月，包括武俠、玄幻、歷史、神話、穿越、傳記、宮鬥等在內所有古裝題材網劇、電視劇、網路大電影都不允許播出，估計受影響的古裝劇超過幾十部以上。亦有人在網上放風，這次會推出新「限古令」，是由於上次禁制宮鬥劇成效不彰，故新一輪措施打擊範圍要更廣。<br />\n<br />\n不過已經在播放中的劇，如陳喬恩主演的《獨孤皇后》可繼續播出，但不能宣傳、不能推薦，也必須從電視台、網路影音平台推薦版面中移除，播到25日大結局後要徹底消失，必須下架。目前另一齣在內地熱播劇《東宮》即已從影音平台推薦戲中消失，不過該劇快播完，影響不大。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n林峯主演的《大潑猴》、迪麗熱巴主演的《三生三世枕上書》、葉童演出的《新白娘子傳奇》及陳道明主演的《慶餘年》等劇原本排好3至6月播出，如今又不知何年何月可以播出。內地突然要全面禁古裝，據內地製作人表示：「自從《延禧攻略》與《如懿傳》被禁一時間允許被播出後，一樣很有話題性，官方就覺得要作出更大範圍去打壓古裝，所以投資古裝風險越來越大。」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果動新聞》訂閱新世代，4月開始免費訂閱，現在接受登記！<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Ja3IXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Ja3IXw&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEJ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=5fee537c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Ja3IXw</a> <br />\n---------------------"},{"pid":"1b7afe49eda2c164d846a9d535dc7c4ebfb6e57a","tid":1074493,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T12:11:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190323/59402995?fbclid=IwAR2RlEwrng5T7LHeE6e4OFDbWn2pjMm-7DsUYNV9BzQnDT1czZULOS9tCmM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190323%2F59402995%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2RlEwrng5T7LHeE6e4OFDbWn2pjMm-7DsUYNV9BzQnDT1czZULOS9tCmM&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEJ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=dc8f76f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190323%2F59402995%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2RlEwrng5T7LHeE6e4OFDbWn2pjMm-7DsUYNV9BzQnDT1czZULOS9tCmM&h=5e3cf95e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190323/59402995?fbclid=IwAR2RlEwrng5T7LHeE6e4OFDbWn2pjMm-7DsUYNV9BzQnDT1czZULOS9tCmM</a>"}]}